MessageFactory<AgentConfiguration,Map<String,Object>>
public class StatementDistributionBeaconMessageFactory
extends BeaconMessageFactory

BeaconMessageFactory extension responsible for producing a beaconable message containing core beacon properties as well as metadata describing the state of the current StatementDistribution being maintained within StatementDistributionRepository.
